        <abstract>
            <p>Regrets J. D. Hooker did not visit Berlin.</p>
            <p>Describes legal difficulties of Ernst Dieffenbach.</p>
            <p>Lists species of Infusoria found in dust samples. Discusses origin of Atlantic dust. Discusses Infusoria in cosmetic paint from Tierra del Fuego and Patagonian earth. Thanks CD for samples. Would like samples from sea-bed.</p>
        </abstract>
